# 1. Executive Overview

The **NEO TURBINE FULL SYSTEM** represents the flagship propulsion architecture within the PI220 ecosystem.

Unlike conventional propulsion systems that treat thermal energy, airflow energy, and hydraulic stabilization as separate engineering domains, the NEO architecture attempts to unify them into a single integrated energy ecosystem.

The design objective is simple:

> Recover energy wherever it exists.
>
> Convert energy whenever possible.
>
> Recycle energy continuously.
>
> Stabilize the structure using the recovered energy.

The system therefore functions simultaneously as:

* Propulsion System
* Energy Recovery System
* Stability System
* Power Generation System
* Flight Optimization System

